\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="NO-BOK" style="mso-ansi-language: NO-BOK;"><b>Gigachansen:</b> Som medlem i v&aring;r kundklubb deltar du automatiskt i v&aring;rt m&aring;natliga t&auml;vling n&auml;r du handlar f&ouml;r &ouml;ver 500 kr.<b> </b></span><span lang="DA" style="mso-ansi-language: DA;">Varje t&auml;vlingsperiod varar fr&aring;n f&ouml;rsta till sista dagen i m&aring;naden. </span><span lang="NO-BOK" style="mso-ansi-language: NO-BOK;">Dragningen sker i slutet av f&ouml;ljande m&aring;nad. </span><span lang="SV" style="mso-ansi-language: SV;">Totalt delas 1000 presentkort ut varje m&aring;nad. Presentkorten &auml;r giltiga i 3 m&aring;nader och kan anv&auml;ndas online och i butik.</span><span lang="NO-BOK" style="mso-ansi-language: NO-BOK;">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="NO-BOK" style="mso-ansi-language: NO-BOK;">Se fullst&auml;ndiga t&auml;vlingsvillkor </span><span style="text-decoration: underline; color: rgb(32, 16, 241);"><a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://smc-link.s4hana.ondemand.com/eu/data-buffer/sap/public/cuan/link/100/E7A8CF9AA0D3105EE288E41B98616202EBF36637?_V_=2&_K11_=C217EE7277DB30FCF6D23F8D54C4C714651D7066&_L54AD1F204_=c2NlbmFyaW89TUxDUEcmdGVuYW50PW15MzAyODkzLnM0aGFuYS5vbmRlbWFuZC5jb20mdGFyZ2V0PWh0dHBzOi8vd3d3LmVsZ2lnYW50ZW4uc2Uva3VuZGtsdWJiL3Zpbm4tcHJlc2VudGtvcnQtdmFyamUtbWFuYWQvdGF2bGluZ3N2aWxsa29yLXByZXNlbnRrb3J0LXV0bG90dG5pbmc%&_K13_=764&_K14_=e226addbf66fd8f1a86dea1897f0084246f989987a4d3c20d8eb0c05cc2d60e4" target="_blank" title="COMPETITION-TERMS" style="color: rgb(32, 16, 241); text-decoration: underline;"><span lang="NO-BOK" style="mso-ansi-language: NO-BOK;">h&auml;r.</span></a></span><b><span style="mso-ansi-language: NO-BOK;"> <span lang="NO-BOK"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="NO-BOK" style="mso-ansi-language: NO-BOK;">Vi har uppdaterat v&aring;r integritetspolicy f&ouml;r att inkludera denna nya aktivitet. Du kan l&auml;sa v&aring;r integritetspolicy </span><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="color: rgb(32, 16, 241); text-decoration: underline;"><a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://smc-link.s4hana.ondemand.com/eu/data-buffer/sap/public/cuan/link/100/E7A8CF9AA0D3105EE288E41B98616202EBF36637?_V_=2&_K11_=C24B35A2A55B5917C1DBC6C713F36E5C46219076&_L54AD1F204_&_K13_=764&_K14_=5849c889b86be7f7fb87af39a150bd225684dfc71e024a9d808b10118f6a9bb9" target="_blank" title="PRIVACYPOLICY" style="color: rgb(32, 16, 241); text-decoration: underline;"><span lang="NO-BOK" style="mso-ansi-language: NO-BOK;">h&auml;r.</span></a></span></span><span lang="NO-BOK" style="mso-ansi-language: NO-BOK;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n</div>\n<div>Vi reserverar oss f&ouml;r skriv- och/eller tekniska fel. Erbjudandena g&auml;ller s&aring; l&auml;nge lagret r&auml;cker.&nbsp;<br>Du f&aring;r detta e-mail eftersom du tidigare godk&auml;nt att Elgiganten f&aring;r skicka erbjudanden och nyheter till dig.<br><a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://smc-link.s4hana.ondemand.com/eu/data-buffer/sap/public/cuan/link/100/E7A8CF9AA0D3105EE288E41B98616202EBF36637?_V_=2&_K11_=FB61CDACA360BE035C1556970D9EB1B8EBDCC618&_L54AD1F204_&_K13_=764&_K14_=1497e01ee24ffded9436d6785b9d74c1f9d10ee3b16fb6e51f809f5c1d2cba7f" target="_blank" title="UNSUBSCRIBE-NEWSLETTER" style="text-decoration: underline; color: #464646;">Klicka h&auml;r</a> f&ouml;r att avprenumerera fr&aring;n v&aring;rt nyhetsbrev.<br>Detta mejl har skickats till: viktorstrindin93@gmail.com&nbsp;<br>&copy; 2025 Elgiganten. Alla r&auml;ttigheter reserverade.</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<!-- Movable Ink Campaign Code -->\n<table width="1" height="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style="font-size: 0px; line-height: 0px;"><img src="http://www.movable-ink-6948.com/p/up/c7d1111646d48ea9/o.gif?mi_u=ed3ee68fb37445559dd5276104c67c9b&mi_ecmp=9830%20%20%20%20%20%20" alt="" width="1" height="1" aria-hidden="true"></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table><