940	20057a55-6b77-4c33-836d-f01c76b283a4	gmail	19a2c6ff078b6986	email	📦 Holiday surcharges take effect today	http://selfnamed.com?utm_source=Selfnamed+Favorites&utm_campaign=cb8977f629-EMAIL_CAMPAIGN_2023_06_13_09_39_COPY_01&utm_medium=email&utm_term=0_-04c9ad3da9-634059167&mc_cid=cb8977f629&mc_eid=UNIQID\r\n\r\n\r\n** ❗Holiday surcharges are now in effect\r\n------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\nDuring the holiday period, carriers apply temporary surcharges to manage peak demand. From October 28 until December 30, all manual and dropshipping orders will include shipping surcharges.\r\n\r\nFor orders with a US destination:\r\n* $0.40 per order\r\n\r\nFor orders with an EU or UK destination:\r\n* €0.15 per kg for standard shipping\r\n* €0.35 per kg for express shipping\r\n\r\nAll surcharges are automatically applied to Selfnamed shipping profiles. Surcharges will automatically expire on December 30. If you’re using your own custom profiles, make sure to review and update them accordingly.\r\nRead more (https://help.selfnamed.com/en/articles/12638905-are-there-any-shipping-surcharges-for-the-2025-holiday-season?utm_source=Selfnamed+Favorites&utm_campaign=cb8977f629-EMAIL_CAMPAIGN_2023_06_13_09_39_COPY_01&utm_medium=email&utm_term=0_-04c9ad3da9-634059167&mc_cid=cb8977f629&mc_eid=UNIQID)\r\nhttps://www.selfnamed.com/en/private-label-products/all?categories=all&ids=104&utm_source=Selfnamed+Favorites&utm_campaign=cb8977f629-EMAIL_CAMPAIGN_2023_06_13_09_39_COPY_01&utm_medium=email&utm_term=0_-04c9ad3da9-634059167&mc_cid=cb8977f629&mc_eid=UNIQID\r\n\r\n\r\n** Order now or miss out on holiday sales 🫨\r\n------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\nThe countdown is on! Make sure your products arrive in time for the biggest sales season of the year. Check the final order deadlines below and place your orders before it’s too late 💪\r\n\r\n\r\n** Black Friday Cyber Monday cut-offs\r\n------------------------------------------------------------\r\nOrder size (units) Cut-off date\r\n1000+              Oct 31\r\n101–1000           Nov 4\r\n21–100             Nov 11\r\n1–20               Nov 18\r\n\r\nOrdering before these dates gives you the best chance to receive your products before BFCM 📈\r\n\r\n\r\n** Christmas cut-offs\r\n------------------------------------------------------------\r\nOrder size (units) Cut-off date\r\n1000+              Nov 26\r\n101–1000           Nov 28\r\n21–100             Dec 5\r\n1–20               Dec 12\r\n\r\nOrdering before these dates gives you the best chance to receive your products before December 25 🎁\r\nOrder now (https://www.selfnamed.com/en/private-label-products/all?categories=all&utm_source=Selfnamed+Favorites&utm_campaign=cb8977f629-EMAIL_CAMPAIGN_2023_06_13_09_39_COPY_01&utm_medium=email&utm_term=0_-04c9ad3da9-634059167&mc_cid=cb8977f629&mc_eid=UNIQID)\r\n\r\nsupport@SELFNAMED.com (mailto:support@SELFNAMED.com)\r\nhttps://facebook.com/self-Named-100164735831479?utm_source=Selfnamed+Favorites&utm_campaign=cb8977f629-EMAIL_CAMPAIGN_2023_06_13_09_39_COPY_01&utm_medium=email&utm_term=0_-04c9ad3da9-634059167&mc_cid=cb8977f629&mc_eid=UNIQID\r\nhttps://www.instagram.com/selfnamed_cosmetics/?utm_source=Selfnamed+Favorites&utm_campaign=cb8977f629-EMAIL_CAMPAIGN_2023_06_13_09_39_COPY_01&utm_medium=email&utm_term=0_-04c9ad3da9-634059167&mc_cid=cb8977f629&mc_eid=UNIQID\r\nhttps://linkedin.com/company/self-named/?utm_source=Selfnamed+Favorites&utm_campaign=cb8977f629-EMAIL_CAMPAIGN_2023_06_13_09_39_COPY_01&utm_medium=email&utm_term=0_-04c9ad3da9-634059167&mc_cid=cb8977f629&mc_eid=UNIQID\r\nhttps://youtube.com/@selfnamed_skincare?utm_source=Selfnamed+Favorites&utm_campaign=cb8977f629-EMAIL_CAMPAIGN_2023_06_13_09_39_COPY_01&utm_medium=email&utm_term=0_-04c9ad3da9-634059167&mc_cid=cb8977f629&mc_eid=UNIQID\r\nhttps://www.tiktok.com/@selfnamed_cosmetics?utm_source=Selfnamed+Favorites&utm_campaign=cb8977f629-EMAIL_CAMPAIGN_2023_06_13_09_39_COPY_01&utm_medium=email&