s to be in Swedish (based on the subject line 'En snabb påminnelse om insättningsgarantin' which translates to 'A quick reminder about the deposit guarantee'). The email body is primarily HTML template code without visible content.", "category": "work/financial", "priority": "medium", "sentiment": "neutral", "actionItems": ["Review deposit guarantee information from Revolut (likely requires opening the full email or clicking through)"]}, "labelIds": ["UNREAD", "CATEGORY_UPDATES", "INBOX"], "threadId": "19a2beab3328a181"}	\N	0.8	2025-10-28 17:43:11	2025-10-29 06:33:30.939
14	20057a55-6b77-4c33-836d-f01c76b283a4	gmail	19a2b5432688006a	email	Ansökan om lån hos LF Finans	<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">\r\n<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">\r\n<head>\r\n<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">\r\n<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no">\r\n<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width; initial-scale=1.0; maximum-scale=1.0; user-scalable=no;">\r\n<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=9; IE=8; IE=7; IE=EDGE">\r\n<style type="text/css">\r\n\t\t@@font-face {\r\n            font-family: 'IntroCondBold';\r\n            src: url('https://innovation.lansforsakringar.se/fonts/intro-cond-bold.woff') format('truetype');\r\n            font-weight: 300;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        #outlook a {\r\n            padding: 0;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        body {\r\n            width: 100% !important;\r\n            -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\r\n            -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;\r\n            margin: 0;\r\n            padding: 0;\r\n            background-color: #fff;\r\n            color: #222;\r\n            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\r\n            font-size: 1rem;\r\n            line-height: 1.45;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .ReadMsgBody {\r\n            width: 100%;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .ExternalClass {\r\n            width: 100%;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .backgroundTable {\r\n            margin: 0 auto;\r\n            padding: 0;\r\n            width: 100% !important;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        table td {\r\n            border-collapse: collapse;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .ExternalClass * {\r\n            line-height: 115%;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .footer {\r\n            border-top: 1px solid #ddd9c3;\r\n            padding-top: 20px;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        h2 {\r\n            color: #005aa0 !important;\r\n            font-weight: bold;\r\n            line-height: 1.35;\r\n            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\r\n\t\t\tfont-size: 36px;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        .ii a[href] {\r\n            color: #fff !important;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n\t\t.btn-table {\r\n            width: 50%;\r\n        }\r\n\t}\r\n    </style><style type="text/css">\r\n        @@media screen and (max-width: 480px) {\r\n            .btn-table {\r\n                width: 75%;\r\n            }\r\n            \r\n            .full {\r\n                width: 100% !important;\r\n                height: auto !important;\r\n            }\r\n            \r\n            .center {\r\n                text-align: center !important;\r\n                width: 100% !important;\r\n                height: auto !important;\r\n            }\r\n\r\n            img.fluid {\r\n                width: 100% !important;\r\n                max-width: 100% !important;\r\n                height: auto !important;\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n    </style>\r\n</head>\r\n<body style="padding:0; margin:0">\r\n<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" class="full" align="center">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top" class="full">\r\n<div>\r\n<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="20" class="full">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top">\r\n<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" class="full">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="left" width="50%" class="full"><img src="cid:Top" alt="Logo" border="0" style="display:block"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" class="full">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td height="35"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="content" style="font-size: 24px !important;">\r\n<h1>Ansökan om lån</h1>\r\n<p>Hej </p>\r\n<p>Tack för din ansökan om lån hos LF Finans. Vi uppskattar ditt intresse för våra tjänster.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Utifrån dina lämnade uppgifter i kreditansökan och information inhämtad via kreditupplysning är vår samlade bedömning att vi tyvärr inte kan bevilja din ansökan.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Har du frågor är du välkommen att kontakta oss på LF Finans på telefon 08-635 37 20. Vi har öppet vardagar 9.00–17.00.\r\n</p>\r\n<p>Vänliga hälsningar <br>\r\nLF Finans </p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td height="35"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="20" class="full">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class="footer" align="center" style="font-size: 16px; color: #848484;"><img src="cid:Logo" height="110" width="600" style="display: block;" class="fluid">\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><i><small>Länsförsäkringar Finans AB (LF Finans) behandlar personuppgifter i enlighet med vad som anges i informationen ”Behandling av personuppgifter” som du hittar på vår webbplats lffinans.se/personuppgifter.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAv säkerhetsskäl kan vi inte besvara frågor via e-post som innehåller hälsouppgifter eller andra känsliga personuppgifter, utan sådana frågor kommer vi i första hand att besvara via post eller via säkra meddelanden på minasidor.lffinans.se.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDetta e-postmeddelande kan innehålla konfidentiell information. Om du har fått meddelandet av misstag, vänligen radera meddelandet utan att spara någon kopia och underrätta avsändaren. Innehållet i meddelandet får inte obehörigen utnyttjas eller röjas.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLänsförsäkringar Finans AB (LF Finans) processes your personal information in accordance with what is stated in the “Processing of personal data” document, which can be found on our website lffinans.se/personuppgifter.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nFor security reasons, we cannot answer questions containing a person’s health details or other sensitive personal data by e-mail. Instead, we will answer these questions by post or via secure messaging at minasidor.lffinans.se.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThis e-mail may contain information that is confidential. If you have received this e-mail in error, please delete it without making any copies and notify the sender. The information in this e-mail may not be used or disclosed without authorization.</small></i></p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>\r\n	{"to": "<viktorstrindin93@gmail.com>", "date": "Tue, 28 Oct 2025 15:58:48 +0100", "from": "\\"LF Finans - Svara ej på denna adress\\" <noreply@lffinans.se>", "snippet": "Ansökan om lån Hej Tack för din ansökan om lån hos LF Finans. Vi uppskattar ditt intresse för våra tjänster. Utifrån dina lämnade uppgifter i kreditansökan och information inhämtad via kreditupplysning", "analysis": {"summary": "This is an automated email from LF Finans (a Swedish financial services company) regarding a loan application. The email appears to be a notification or confirmation related to a loan application process with LF Finans.", "category": "work/financial", "priority": "high", "sentiment": "neutral", "actionItems": ["Review loan application details from LF Finans", "Follow any instructions in the email body (content not fully visible in provided excerpt)"]}, "labelIds": ["IMPORTANT", "CATEGORY_PERSONAL", "INBOX"], "threadId": "19a2b5432688006a"}	\N	1	2025-10-28 14:58:48	2025-10-29 06:34:31.768
34	20057a55-6b77-4c33-836d-f01c76b283a4	gmail	19a29f995bb16751	email	Nuevos anuncios hoy		{"to": "viktorstrindin93@gmail.com", "date": "Tue, 28 Oct 2025 09:40:13 +0100 (CET)", "from": "idealista <noresponder@idealista.com>", "snippet": "Te enviamos 5 novedades de tu búsqueda guardada. Hola, Viltor, Te enviamos 5 novedades de tu búsqueda guardada. Viviendas en tu zona personalizada Todos los precios Sin otros filtros Piso en plaza de", "analysis": {"summary": "This is an automated notification email from Idealista, a real estate platform, alerting the recipient about new property listings posted today. The email contains minimal content and is part of their regular property alert service.", "category": "newsletter", "priority": "low", "sentiment": "neutral", "actionItems": ["Review new property listings on Idealista platform if actively searching for real estate"]}, "labelIds": ["UNREAD", "CATEGORY_UPDATES", "INBOX"], "threadId": "19a29f995bb16751"}	\N	0.49999999999999994	2025-10-28 08:40:13	2025-10-29 06:36:04.085
