24	20057a55-6b77-4c33-836d-f01c76b283a4	gmail	19a2ad2e2bbc6406	email	What's new in Runway: Introducing Apps and Workflows	Even more ways to create anything with Runway.   Runway logo\nwhite \n( https://clicks.runwayml.com/f/a/94Rr-k-B5PjFVhT8nj7XjA~~/AAQRxRA~/U8_MFHDMpVY8C2nmvyEuWuLcqu6jAaAE4v5roF0W7GcFgwQyjVI22Ew4ZtD0mzrPYmQ8zbFGOx8qCCWzKqJy8uImqCmgMuPpyhvRVmsHUNWurouw1gRBaaJJmkyxEenFkuIZfSkadILugY3jyAseDuYljXo2IjiB0GCCaSt8gHV6c88EumLsbf-oPW_PExp8 )\n\n\n******************************\nGet to know Apps and Workflows\n******************************\n\n*****************************************************************\nCatch up on our latest releases, including our all-new Apps and\nWorkflows.\n\n*****************************************************************\n\nOpen Runway  \n( https://clicks.runwayml.com/f/a/af96xIyw1dmcNCtIFVjb4Q~~/AAQRxRA~/1KuoVWXA5V_QIhWSi_d28t9jOPcoRgpOnTHaW6ee_S-rhQhfPO2w_7BC9Tjo5pKswCtNzRrEi84xrw8jS6AlsKEA_BNQXt-Rph72djpbDdEJX2U0VNiv0zwy9DcrS11fKiZGYmwmjcvvIlftrV9RPv2tzvSnPyrUL7zBdzxSsfbH5yaSubaRQyDUFbGHLhEO )\n\n\n****************\nIntroducing Apps\n****************\n\n********************************************\nAn easier way to create anything with Runway\n********************************************\n\n*****************************************************************\nFrom reshooting your products to restyling images, Apps are an\never-growing collection of use case specific workflows that make\nit easier than ever to get to great outputs.\n\nApps are now rolling out on web, with more releasing every week.\nHave an app idea you’d like to see? Let us know on social.\n*****************************************************************\n\nBrowse Apps  \n( https://clicks.runwayml.com/f/a/7nmHoHtaFooriL9olp7a6w~~/AAQRxRA~/ZEgDKYbjrT7XvJAF8lgq7govHRMytqWR6VasjSJUuOGEo3GEyRmF6dnIeIvqjStqIF0PKhGiFzNFC6dKP0IyucYmbOwNbDkmZvmLPXBxZgLXP1c6TWWUtj4qGhCXhxKrCUYtV8eljltCTK5HzSDeVQeC6fcyDgx4vlPACOcCrPXQBP2dF-sgGv1FxWr2aOumjsTWvntYf5rEJK8pkNL_FA~~ )\n\n\n*