89	20057a55-6b77-4c33-836d-f01c76b283a4	gmail	19a21f2314f20b60	email	I wanna hear what you do with this ❤️	Hey ,\r\n\r\nI can't believe it's almost time...\r\n \r\n \r\nWith everything coming together for DESTINY this Friday, it’s been exciting to look back on the journey.\r\n \r\n \r\nAlong the way, there have been a few goodies that not everyone’s had a chance to see yet.\r\n \r\n \r\nIf you’re curious, [I left everything here for you before they go.](https://cymatics.fm/pages/destiny-secret-expansion-thank-2025)\r\n \r\n \r\nTalk soon,\r\nSteven\r\n \r\n \r\nP.S. Waiting List members always get in before the public, so joining is the safest bet if you want access this Friday.\r\n \r\n \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n \r\n \r\n\r\n \r\n \r\n\r\nYou received this email from Cymatics.fm. If you would like to unsubscribe, [click here](https://manage.kmail-lists.com/subscriptions/unsubscribe?a=UXzVXV&c=01K20A0VM1W7GG0GCRSF3BTWS9&k=c93fb7a8a73bb36fdf07e8822878312d&m=01K8GWQK016TY7PA1WJ03RVMQR&r=01K8GY8GZMM5XD50NZ2CDJZ5G5).	{"to": "viktorstrindin93@gmail.com", "date": "Sun, 26 Oct 2025 19:15:10 +0000 (UTC)", "from": "Steven Cymatics <team@sounds.cymatics.fm>", "snippet": "Hey , I can&#39;t believe it&#39;s almost time... With everything coming together for DESTINY this Friday, it&#39;s been exciting to look back on the journey. Along the way, there have been a few", "analysis": {"summary": "Marketing email from Cymatics (music production company) promoting an upcoming product launch called 'DESTINY' scheduled for Friday. Steven is offering early access to exclusive content and encouraging recipients to join the waiting list for priority access.", "category": "newsletter", "priority": "low", "sentiment": "positive", "actionItems": ["Review exclusive content at provided link if interested", "Join waiting list before Friday for early access to DESTINY product"]}, "labelIds": ["UNREAD", "CATEGORY_UPDATES", "INBOX"], "threadId": "19a21f2314f20b60"}	\N	0.