2	20057a55-6b77-4c33-836d-f01c76b283a4	gmail	19a2be6455650389	email	[Action required] Claude Sonnet 3.5 v2 is now retired	Migrate to Claude Sonnet 4.5 to avoid service interruption.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nHello,\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nEffective today, Anthropic has retired and no longer supports Claude Sonnet \r\n3.5 v2 (claude-3-5-sonnet-20241022)natively on the Claude API. All requests to \r\nClaude Sonnet 3.5 v2 will now return an error.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nWe regularly retire earlier models to prioritize serving customers our most \r\ncapable, highest quality models. Please see ourdeprecation policy \r\n<https://docs.claude.com/en/docs/about-claude/model-deprecations> to learn more.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nTo avoid further service interruption, you must upgrade to a newer, supported \r\nmodel. We recommend upgrading toClaude Sonnet 4.5 \r\n<https://docs.claude.com/en/docs/about-claude/models#model-comparison-table>, \r\nwhich offers significantly improved intelligence at the same price. We also \r\nofferClaude Haiku 4.5 \r\n<https://docs.claude.com/en/docs/about-claude/models#model-comparison-table>, \r\nwhich offers near-frontier performance at one-third the cost. \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nTo get started with upgrading to our latest models, please explore our \r\ndeveloper docs <https://docs.claude.com/en/docs/about-claude/models/overview>.\r\n\r\n\r\nIf you have questions or require assistance, please reach out to our support \r\nteam via the message icon in the lower right corner of ourHelp Center \r\n<https://support.claude.com/en/articles/8114535-where-can-i-go-for-api-support-and-assistance>\r\n.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n <https://www.anthropic.com/?utm_source=email>\r\n\r\n <https://x.com/claudeai> <https://www.linkedin.com/showcase/claude/> \r\n<https://www.youtube.com/@anthropic-ai>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nThis email was sent to viktorstrindin93@gmail.com.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nAnthropic PBC, 548 Market St, PMB 90375, San Francisco, CA 94104 \r\n	{"to": "viktorstrindin93@gmail.