\r\n➡️ New export as PNG feature for easy sharing\r\n \r\nThese updates make CopyCoder more powerful and flexible than ever!\r\n \r\n \r\n\r\nTry the new features [https://copycoder.ai/]\r\n\r\n \r\nLet us know what you think!\r\n\r\n— Moritz\r\nYou are receiving this email because you opted-in to receive updates from CopyCoder\r\nCopyCoder, 71-75 Shelton Street, Covent Garden, London, United Kingdom, WC2H 9JQ\r\nUnsubscribe [https://app.loops.so/unsubscribe/cmh98rabo019k01lhgk1mgshd/73d57b689411426f302fb6cbba34b6937b566e0fca68e05476be6d20a5df93a5]\r\n	{"to": "viktorstrindin93@gmail.com", "date": "Mon, 27 Oct 2025 14:36:55 +0000", "from": "Moritz at CopyCoder <moritz@copycoderai.com>", "snippet": "Plus other big updates ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏​ ͏", "analysis": {"summary": "CopyCoder has released major product updates including a new Mobile App Mode for designing mobile screens, a Components + Reference feature for extracting and reusing design elements, and a complete canvas redesign. Additional improvements include faster design generation and PNG export functionality.", "category": "newsletter", "priority": "low", "sentiment": "positive", "actionItems": ["Try the new Mobile App Mode feature", "Test the Components + Reference feature for extracting design elements", "Explore the redesigned canvas experience", "Provide feedback on the new features"]}, "labelIds": ["UNREAD", "CATEGORY_UPDATES", "INBOX"], "threadId": "19a2619ccac2bb38"}	\N	0.49999999999999994	2025-10-27 14:36:55	2025-10-29 06:37:47.562
